<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 02:25:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>数十架 A-10 疣猪似乎准备加入 Epic Fury</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/dozens-of-a-10-warthogs-appear-poised-to-join-epic-fury</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在部署更多疣猪之际，越来越多的迹象表明伊朗领土上的地面行动可能很快就会发生。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/dozens-of-a-10-warthogs-appear-poised-to-join-epic-fury"&gt;数十架 A-10 疣猪似乎准备加入史诗之怒的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 22:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/dozens-of-a-10-warthogs-appear-poised-to-join-epic-fury</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰使用私人防空队保护工业免受俄罗斯无人机的攻击</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-using-private-air-defense-teams-to-protect-industry-against-russian-drones</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰希望通过动员私营部门来减轻其部队的防空负担，同时扩大覆盖范围。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-using-private-air-defense-teams-to-protect-industry-against-russian-drones"&gt;乌克兰使用私人防空队保护工业免受俄罗斯无人机攻击的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 20:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/ukraine-using-private-air-defense-teams-to-protect-industry-against-russian-drones</guid></item><item><title>A-10 疣猪机在伊拉克进行奇怪的长时间扫射</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-doing-bizarrely-long-strafing-runs-in-iraq</link><description>&lt;p&gt;A-10 进行九秒长的射击绝对不正常。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-doing-bizarrely-long-strafing-runs-in-iraq"&gt;A-10 疣猪在伊拉克进行奇怪的长时间扫射&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 18:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/a-10-warthogs-are-doing-bizarrely-long-strafing-runs-in-iraq</guid></item><item><title>以色列 F-16 战机似乎携带集束弹药</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/israeli-f-16s-appear-to-be-carrying-cluster-munitions</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这些集束弹药可能有一个非常特殊的目的，旨在削弱伊朗发射远程弹道导弹的能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/israeli-f-16s-appear-to-be-carrying-cluster-munitions"&gt;以色列 F-16 战机似乎携带集束弹药&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 18:19:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/israeli-f-16s-appear-to-be-carrying-cluster-munitions</guid></item><item><title>图片显示 E-3 哨兵在伊朗袭击中被完全摧毁（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/images-purportedly-show-e-3-sentry-totally-destroyed-from-iranian-strike</link><description>&lt;p&gt;失去一架 E-3 对于机身日益摇摇欲坠的日益萎缩的机队来说是一个重大打击，并表明了其他能力和防御方面的差距。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/images-purportedly-show-e-3-sentry-totally-destroyed-from-iranian-strike"&gt;图片显示 E-3 哨兵在伊朗袭击中被完全摧毁（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 17:40:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/images-purportedly-show-e-3-sentry-totally-destroyed-from-iranian-strike</guid></item><item><title>美国正在以惊人的速度消耗战斧巡航导弹库存：报告</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-is-burning-through-tomahawk-cruise-missile-stockpile-at-a-alarming-rate-report</link><description>&lt;p&gt;官员称，迄今为止，与伊朗的冲突已消耗了超过 850 枚战斧导弹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-is-burning-through-tomahawk-cruise-missile-stockpile-at-a-alarming-rate-report"&gt;《美国正在以惊人的速度消耗战斧巡航导弹库存：报告》&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 02:45:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-is-burning-through-tomahawk-cruise-missile-stockpile-at-a-alarming-rate-report</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-185</link><description>&lt;p&gt;还记得阳光照射的感觉吗？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-185"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 22:24:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-185</guid></item><item><title>乌代德空军基地正在寻找加固的地下设施</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-underground-facilities-now-being-sought-for-al-udeid-air-base</link><description>&lt;p&gt;伊朗的袭击凸显了加强基础设施和避难所以保护部队和军事资产的迫切需要。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-underground-facilities-now-being-sought-for-al-udeid-air-base"&gt;正在为乌代德空军基地寻找的加固地下设施&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 19:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-underground-facilities-now-being-sought-for-al-udeid-air-base</guid></item><item><title>私人 F-5 敌方喷气机与海军战斗机飞行员展开战斗</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/private-f-5-adversary-jets-taking-the-fight-to-navy-fighter-pilots</link><description>&lt;p&gt;TWZ 特别通道：我们参观了 TacAir，了解他们大幅升级的 F-5AT 战斗机，以及他们如何复制敌机以保持美国战斗机机组人员的敏捷性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/private-f-5-adversary-jets-taking-the-fight-to-navy-fighter-pilots"&gt;私人 F-5 敌方喷气机与海军战斗机飞行员作战后，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 17:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/private-f-5-adversary-jets-taking-the-fight-to-navy-fighter-pilots</guid></item><item><title>美国是否会投放地雷来阻止伊朗导弹发射器？</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/is-the-u-s-dropping-anti-tank-mines-to-stop-iranian-missile-launchers</link><description>&lt;p&gt;为了进一步削弱伊朗的发射能力，在远程导弹设施和发射点周围布设地雷是有意义的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/is-the-u-s-dropping-anti-tank-mines-to-stop-iranian-missile-launchers"&gt;美国是否会投放地雷来阻止伊朗导弹发射器？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 01:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/is-the-u-s-dropping-anti-tank-mines-to-stop-iranian-missile-launchers</guid></item></channel></rss>